definitions.definition: Washed by the waves or tide (of a rock or strip of shore, or of an anchor , etc., when flush with the surface of the water, so that the waves break over it); covered with water.
Covered , overspread ( with or in something).

main_definition: Washed by the waves or tide (of a rock or strip of shore, or of an anchor , etc., when flush with the surface of the water, so that the waves break over it); covered with water.
secondary_definitions: ( by extension ) Covered , overspread ( with or in something).
